{"tid":1372984,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解今日D巴絲............","createTime":"2019-07-27T14:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T14:23:37.000Z","uid":41914,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c090c2df573c759a69f45cb4ef43e47a76a7f97f","tid":1372984,"uid":41914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:16:31.000Z","msg":"........<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可以咁撚高質?</span></span><br />\n俾狗圍個陣 大家都好冷靜冇亂衝, 最多係互罵下....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇一個市民,冇一間鋪頭被破壞, 反而D狗亂射TEARGAS, 屌你老母仲射去老人院? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對面放TEARGAS, 勇武既前線冇退避, 硬食, 執起掉返轉頭都仲有.......心諗你地唔係進化到咁勁下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾狗噴野, 我見有巴打勇到硬食照打, 都衝上前打狗.....勁到文字都表達唔到.... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到搵到有車入面有兵器, 大家都好冷靜搵記宿影低, 大叫唔好掂.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到撤退個陣保謢市民走, 1212 退後個陣, 我真係見到HK人個種齊心.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n退到月台個刻, 有畜龍, D市民手拖手組起防線保謢最後離開既人.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我屌你地咩.....齊心到咁, 睇住D畫面我喊左出黎.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我今日想好大聲咁講, 我好RESPECT各位巴打絲打!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望大家休息完, 一齊再上路!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽日見!<br />\n<br />\n另外,我想多謝各位記者, 有你地既公平觀察, D狗先唔敢亂黎, 如果你地有受左傷既話, 祝早日康服! 另外D仆街狗係度開大燈照你地, 大家知咩事啦, 心照, 做埋呢D小動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武組辛苦了!! 而家係文宣組做野既時間啦!!!!</span>"},{"pid":"0e023f6265